{"info": {"author": "Indigames", "author_email": "dev@indigames.net", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: Microsoft :: Windows", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Topic :: Games/Entertainment"], "description": "# igeOpenAL\n\nC++ extension OpenAL sound for 3D and 2D games.\n\nYou can install it using the PyPI:\n\n\tpip install igeOpenAL\n\n### Features\n- (ogg , wav) extension are supported\n- Preload supported\n\n### Functions\n# First, you need to import and init the sound system\n```python\nimport pyxopenal\n\nsound = pyxopenal.sound()\nsound.init()\n```\n\n# Play the sound\n```python\n# (sound_name , loop)\nsound.play('sound/beep2.ogg', False)\n```\n# Release it when everything is done\n```python\nsound.release()\n```\n# 3D sound optional\n- Global\n```python\n# (option)\nsound.setListenerPosition(0, 0, -10);\nsound.setListenerOrientation(0, 0, -10, 0, -1.0, 0);\n```\n- Local\n```python\n# (sound_name , option)\nsound.setPositon('sound/beep2.ogg', 0, 0, -10);\nsound.setPitch('sound/beep2.ogg', 1.1);\nsound.setGain('sound/beep2.ogg', 1.1);\nsound.setRolloff('sound/beep2.ogg', 1.1);\n```\n\n### Todo\n- To support streaming\n- Sound packing strucure\n\n### Reference\n- [OpenAL](https://www.openal.org/)\n- [OpenAL Soft](https://github.com/kcat/openal-soft) - a software implementation of the OpenAL 3D audio API.\n- [Xiph](https://xiph.org/) - Ogg loader\n\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://indigames.net/", "keywords": "OpenAL 3D game Xiph ogg vorbis opus sound playback audio indigames", "license": "MIT", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "igeOpenAL", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/igeOpenAL/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/igeOpenAL/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://indigames.net/"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/igeOpenAL/0.0.3/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": "", "summary": "C++ extension OpenAL sound for 3D and 2D games.", "version": "0.0.3", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>igeOpenAL</h1>\n<p>C++ extension OpenAL sound for 3D and 2D games.</p>\n<p>You can install it using the PyPI:</p>\n<pre><code>pip install igeOpenAL\n</code></pre>\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>(ogg , wav) extension are supported</li>\n<li>Preload supported</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Functions</h3>\n<h1>First, you need to import and init the sound system</h1>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">pyxopenal</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">sound</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">pyxopenal</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">init</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n</pre>\n<h1>Play the sound</h1>\n<pre><span class=\"c1\"># (sound_name , loop)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">play</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'sound/beep2.ogg'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kc\">False</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<h1>Release it when everything is done</h1>\n<pre><span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">release</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n</pre>\n<h1>3D sound optional</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Global</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><span class=\"c1\"># (option)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">setListenerPosition</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">setListenerOrientation</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">1.0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n</pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Local</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><span class=\"c1\"># (sound_name , option)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">setPositon</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'sound/beep2.ogg'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">setPitch</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'sound/beep2.ogg'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mf\">1.1</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">setGain</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'sound/beep2.ogg'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mf\">1.1</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sound</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">setRolloff</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'sound/beep2.ogg'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mf\">1.1</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n</pre>\n<h3>Todo</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>To support streaming</li>\n<li>Sound packing strucure</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Reference</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.openal.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OpenAL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/kcat/openal-soft\" rel=\"nofollow\">OpenAL Soft</a> - a software implementation of the OpenAL 3D audio API.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://xiph.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Xiph</a> - Ogg loader</li>\n</ul>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6270321, "releases": {"0.0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "cf05aaf8c824ac009b5c987c90219e37", "sha256": "3f61b21a284a3fde115ff87ef27a96914ff4c051e5b189e4b5b57c85667eca97"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "igeOpenAL-0.0.1-cp37-cp37m-win32.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "cf05aaf8c824ac009b5c987c90219e37", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "cp37", "requires_python": null, "size": 947331, "upload_time": "2019-11-15T09:02:34", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-11-15T09:02:34.509038Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/d7/aa/519aa6ffa4d06279130d5e3232953c9ad1bdf7aa7d823e8df048b8087ed5/igeOpenAL-0.0.1-cp37-cp37m-win32.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "fd31d1d3f302f51bc09a0456f7aac9eb", "sha256": "d86b6e07e71edb3d4372287a3bb192fc89c8845e621a8355fc0dd6b590c3703b"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "igeOpenAL-0.0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "fd31d1d3f302f51bc09a0456f7aac9eb", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 2038064, "upload_time": "2019-11-15T09:02:37", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-11-15T09:02:37.861002Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/0c/48/5b1afe3c8aac3c54b3f6b9920458e9adf4b65886ff38fd0513c1f743a113/igeOpenAL-0.0.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.0.2": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "0477d2dfb2ab5ba9625f010108cb56a1", "sha256": "2a81bff5dae5ed1ba1fbdc6ae5869aad01d2e8c5853e3f0d345c14be88a7cb9a"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "igeOpenAL-0.0.2-cp37-cp37m-win32.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "0477d2dfb2ab5ba9625f010108cb56a1", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "cp37", "requires_python": null, "size": 947327, "upload_time": "2019-11-15T09:44:13", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-11-15T09:44:13.617578Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/83/f0/096e8da11e19be